text: Matey Kaziyski (; born 23 September 1984) is a Bulgarian volleyball player. He was a member of Bulgaria men's national volleyball team in 2003-2012 and Japanese club Panasonic Panthers, a participant of the Olympic Games Beijing 2008, bronze medalist of the World Championship 2006, World Cup 2007 and European Championship 2009. He is a multiple winner of the CEV Champions League and FIVB Club World Championship with the Italian club Trentino Volley. ==Other websites== * FIVB profile Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:2008 Summer Olympics Category:Olympians for Bulgaria Category:Bulgarian volleyball players
